trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to a <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"></xref>, an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"></xref> or an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 表示可扩展性元素添加到<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimePart"> </xref>、 <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding"> </xref>或<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: It specifies the schema for XML messages that are not SOAP compliant.
trans-unit.target: 它指定不符合的 SOAP 的 XML 消息的架构。

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: 有关指定的 XML Web 服务协议的详细信息，请参阅[[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices&1;>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c)。

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: 有关 Web 服务描述语言 (WSDL) 的详细信息，请参阅在 http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/ 规范。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding"></xref> class.
Gets or sets the name of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref> to which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding"></xref> applies.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置的名称<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart"></xref>到<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.MimeXmlBinding"></xref>适用。

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
